{"tid":1361818,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"區塊鏈 decentralized 論壇 有冇得諗","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T03:47:46.000Z","uid":264097,"like":83,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd17f5945bb4f6c57c684fbb52f38b8ee9682a0","tid":1361818,"uid":264097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:42:44.000Z","msg":"雖然唔太可能發生 萬一中共搞連登 都會幾麻煩 早有兩手準備好啲<br />\n<br />\n基本上個提議就係 用區塊鏈嘅技術 整個論壇出嚟 咁基本上就唔會有中央伺服器 畀人ddos 其餘嘅嘢大致上同連登一樣  可能 email authentication 仲係需要一個server 不過其餘嘅嘢 就儲存喺區塊鏈<br />\n<br />\n討論下個可行性<br />\n<br />\n睇下連登團隊有冇興趣整<br />\n又或者有冇其他巴絲有興趣一齊整個open source project"},{"pid":"55a508d92b93585121457b046fc648aac5432479","tid":1361818,"uid":264097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a0963cddfd0c7c4bd2c930d2f40efb8f3aacc305","tid":1361818,"uid":281189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:17:45.000Z","msg":"推，呢樣嘢唔急<br />\n但都要慢慢諗定"},{"pid":"9527ca31309446021abc69c88d99fc460634d521","tid":1361818,"uid":281189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲熟區塊鏈講解吓"},{"pid":"01e7ae886c90a3fc0dfd2771cc96b1343d0b167a","tid":1361818,"uid":251083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:32:06.000Z","msg":"雖然唔識，照推"},{"pid":"857b1ce9846f3dd1e23f95f2c099e28f0773f1e5","tid":1361818,"uid":226562,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:34:10.000Z","msg":"區塊連技術上可行<br />\n但係有幾個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點del po？<br />\n對方係咪可以用 51% 算力收我地皮？<br />\nblochchain 係每個 transaction 都要全network機認證，連登嘅流量好難應付<br />\n同埋點反五毛"},{"pid":"53a0c90615416baa873e2b89ee07126df18c6ea9","tid":1361818,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"zeronet?"},{"pid":"a488a0599534a83dc725de5a4974ce723d976ea0","tid":1361818,"uid":235437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"857b1ce9846f3dd1e23f95f2c099e28f0773f1e5","tid":1361818,"uid":226562,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:34:10.000Z","msg":"區塊連技術上可行<br />\n但係有幾個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點del po？<br />\n對方係咪可以用 51% 算力收我地皮？<br />\nblochchain 係每個 transaction 都要全network機認證，連登嘅流量好難應付<br />\n同埋點反五毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:46:28.000Z","msg":"Agger, 唔太識details, 但點樣ensure miners 數量唔會被佢地control over 50%? <br />\n<br />\nBitcoin 個啲就話有好多nodes, 所以好難override 個P2P network 姐<br />\n<br />\n利申：新手，有錯請屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d71b52572a48407b4f5bc0cfd136d5f02553e5","tid":1361818,"uid":67527,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T20:19:20.000Z","msg":"個transaction嘅latency絕對冇連登咁快，同埋宜家blockchain嘅qps亦都冇可能去到連登咁高。<br />\n<br />\n而且blockchain會令到宜家delete post/comment嘅可能性冇咗<br />\n<br />\n一個decentralised嘅system唔係唔work，只係又未能確保資料正確<br />\n<br />\n反而decentralised嘅messenger可能性可能更大，server只做routing，加e2e encryption，咁樣比較難針對性咁attack某啲message"},{"pid":"af5809ccb11b5d797bb3b4fb7b046ceccc3666bc","tid":1361818,"uid":289043,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T21:02:11.000Z","msg":"首先，唔係講親 blockchain 就有 miner。<br />\n<br />\n一講 miner，即係講緊 consensus algorithm 係 Proof-of-Work（PoW）嘅 blockchain，例如 BitCoin 同 Ethereum。宜家 consensus algorithms 五花百門，PoW 只係其中一種。以一個「大家都唔信大家」嘅情況下，PoW 依然仲係公認最好嘅辦法三甲之內。但係用 PoW 好嘥電之餘，transaction rate 仲好低，絕對應付唔到連登嘅流量。<br />\n<br />\n用公開性嚟分，blockchain 有分 public 同 private；用可連接性嚟分，blockchain 有分 permissioned 同 permission-less。而 BitCoin 同 Ethereum 都係 public permission-less 嘅。<br />\n<br />\n如果連登要用 blockchain 嚟 implement，我認為可以考慮用 Delegated Proof-of-Stake (DPoS) 嚟運作。簡單咁講，即係：<br />\n1. Admins 自己要開住部 server（以現有資源即可）<br />\n2. 一部份嘅巴打絲打們亦都要開住部機（自願性質，越多人開越好）<br />\n3. 主 server 同各巴打絲打嘅電腦都要安裝同一個程式（blockchain 主程式）<br />\n<br />\n再講落去會比較複雜。先講吓問題先：<br />\n1. 到底宜家仲有幾多人用緊電腦？<br />\n2. 有電腦嘅巴打絲打們，願唔願意長開部機？<br />\n3. 願意長開部機嘅巴打絲打們信唔信得過 LIHKG 個程式？始終要晌電腦 run，唔同晌手機，無 sandbox 個喎&hellip;<br />\n4. 要開發個 blockchain 程式，成本都好大，而且需要極專業嘅知識，有足夠巴絲參與嗎？"},{"pid":"2eec50a10ec74c6a541d63638de8eb3ffb9dc23b","tid":1361818,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T21:09:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"895b21ca598152929404655baa147bd4bd84b3e5","tid":1361818,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T21:15:23.000Z","msg":"類似 nosql concept 或者 irc 會唔會簡單啲？<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_Relay_Chat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FInternet_Relay_Chat&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0GiIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=cf56244f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_Relay_Chat</a>"},{"pid":"c71ab4af55df610ba0b621a0c433a31cc0b75913","tid":1361818,"uid":272942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T21:17:05.000Z","msg":"好天斬定落雨柴"},{"pid":"dde52e7352262bb658172d869ab04ec61b8c5207","tid":1361818,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T21:21:38.000Z","msg":"可以想像到會超級慢....<br />\n同埋decentralized嘅話好多技術上嘅嘢(database)都要用原始方法重新寫過晒<br />\ncheck下現行嘅做法都係tor/i2p隱身 // freenet 分散資料<br />\n但都難以做到連登效果<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔係專家 或者有人可以解答到"},{"pid":"0bda51e87abdf6919de0ffec279d9e60e27f4b63","tid":1361818,"uid":66276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T21:28:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c218c876a4219fb03ead9edd7e54ecbd40eb26a4","tid":1361818,"uid":66276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T21:30:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66ca7537a924aaa322e77da86d56b710fcea1588","tid":1361818,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"895b21ca598152929404655baa147bd4bd84b3e5","tid":1361818,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s