er（以現有資源即可）<br />\n2. 一部份嘅巴打絲打們亦都要開住部機（自願性質，越多人開越好）<br />\n3. 主 server 同各巴打絲打嘅電腦都要安裝同一個程式（blockchain 主程式）<br />\n<br />\n再講落去會比較複雜。先講吓問題先：<br />\n1. 到底宜家仲有幾多人用緊電腦？<br />\n2. 有電腦嘅巴打絲打們，願唔願意長開部機？<br />\n3. 願意長開部機嘅巴打絲打們信唔信得過 LIHKG 個程式？始終要晌電腦 run，唔同晌手機，無 sandbox 個喎&hellip;<br />\n4. 要開發個 blockchain 程式，成本都好大，而且需要極專業嘅知識，有足夠巴絲參與嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"用過tendermint做過類似既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有 用blockchain做要考慮好多野<br />\nfrontend web static野用埋IPFS去host會更好"},{"pid":"207c0fbbdb4c55090b560c2b4cebff7df0370651","tid":1361818,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b6378363220043fd37419530d7521b7db54fef2","tid":1361818,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e19dab676c20b426567b548ab67e452d43206542","tid":1361818,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa09166799ed3a9b686fc75a42a8bd8a4f6e305c","tid":1361818,"uid":29218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"del 唔到post 已經唔得啦<br />\n求祈有個post 犯法已經封壇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"Block chain decentralize點封"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:04:04.000Z","msg":"Block domain 囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"開多幾個垃圾domain囉"},{"pid":"a0c605c41a1d1441adaeffff1a4110db1d226635","tid":1361818,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"207c0fbbdb4c55090b560c2b4cebff7df0370651","tid":1361818,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b6378363220043fd37419530d7521b7db54fef2","tid":1361818,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e19dab676c20b426567b548ab67e452d43206542","tid":1361818,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"Block chain decentralize點封"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:04:04.000Z","msg":"Block domain 囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:22:44.000